node.text: @makanwarrior 😂😂 you also la! Nv share with me, only take nice pic to tempt me . Tsk tsk
@makanwarrior thanks for enjoying our Pomegranate Oolong 😃🥤

@supplydemandorchard 
You can always assure that quality come first when you dine in or in this case dine out at @supplydemandorchard! Yes! Even when you order via food delivery!
🔻
The good news is that now you can enjoy @supplydemandorchard delivery menu at 25% off, with free delivery of min. spend $68 (otherwise it's $12 flat rate)!
🔻
We had items from the classic menu and they sure did not disappoint! The star being the ‘La Mattina Dopo which is a 2 in 1 pizza certainly taste as good as it looks! Something that i highly recommend is the Maiale Orientale which is a oriental inspired Pasta that although looks simple, it is actually Amazing! Other items are the Truffle Yakitori Rice and the one and only, Garlic Truffle Fries!
🔻
Incase you are wondering, Yes! That’s a bbt! (2nd page) Pomegranate Oolong Boba Tea to be exact which is exclusive on FoodPanda Delivery!
🔻
Delivery is available during these timings.
Mon – Sat: 11:30am to 8:30pm
Sun: 11:30am to 7:30pm
Call 6734 9588 or WhatsApp at 8369 6887 to place your orders!
